Well met. I'm {c2}Cyrus Bearwolf{/c}, the captain of the guard for Meia forest. You look exhausted... Are you alright? You got to be quite a tough cookie. The Union of Fury may attack at any moment. That said, I must ask if you've seen a soldier on your way here? His name is {c2}Rios Demian{/c}... I have lost all contact with him for some time. He volunteered for a dangerous operation but... I should have stopped him. He was fighting for 36 hours straight before that. If you see him, tell him to return. I know won't be easy. Please help me out here. 
{c5}(He bows and asks for your assistance.){/c}
{c5}(This soldier seems to have a great commander who cared for his subordinates... You promise to deliver the message when you see him){/c}
Thank you. Warrior... Be careful. Your life is valuable. A kingdom's true powers are the soldiers who stand by its flag.

{c5}On this dead body is a letter clutched in its cold hands... According to the letter he is the one whom {/c}{c2}Cyrus Bearwolf{/c}{c5} has been looking for... You read the letter. 
"Currently, the water supplies for the soldiers stationed at Meia forest has been getting brackish because of the {/c}{c1}Harpy Wind Wizard{/c}{c5}s that have set up shop recently. Because of this, an accurate investigation of the situation is required. I recommend that rangers are dispatched into the forest proper. Lethal force is authorized in this investigation if contact is made with the enemy. The most important role for the mission is stay alive. If you believe your life is in jeopardy, return immediately and report your findings. Good luck."
This letter talks about his love for his comrades. From the look of the body and the area around it, there was a big battle. I cannot let his death be in vain. He laid down his life to protect the others in his unit. {c5}I must deliver this message{/c} to {c2}Cyrus Bearwolf{/c}.{/c}

I like you. My name is {c2}Chris Celina{/c}. I often hire adventurers to get the materials I need for my crafts. However, most promise the stars and give up before they finish or come up with lame ideas like "installments". I like strong, capable men. For this... you look pretty much up to the task. I'd like to see how well you perform. What do you think? Would you give it a go? I'll reward you pretty well. 
{c5}(Let me show you what I can do.){/c}
Good, you look dependable enough. Hmm... Like, so here is the quest- My sister and I enjoy perfumes. I totally do. I really have this desire for {c3}Spirit Lost{/c}. It just takes away my mind simply by its magical scent. The perfume, I want to get a bottle to figure it out. I'm sure you'll understand when you see it, for sure. The problem is the route... I heard that it can be obtained from the north western Black Breath. I'm really counting on you here!

