What timing. After you left, {c2}Chris Celina{/c} came by. I don't know how she figured out my distaste for having to indirectly rewarding you. She then searched through our army surplus inventories and told me that she would recommend an item with a letter. This must be it. 
{c5}(He started reading the reward list){/c}
Hmmm... Will this be alright? I want to reward you better. My troops also seem to hold you in high regard for your service. Anyway... Here we are. Pick any one from here. If you ever are looking for an army to join... would you consider joining this one? I will make one position open for you anytime you'd consider serving with us. Thank you.

