Haha...Alright? I'm actually relieved! Didn't I tell you before that it was all in the past? Best not to dwell on it. From what you've told me, sounds like he had a hard time. I'm happy to hear about his good health and that he wants repentance. Can you tell him that I forgive him? He shouldn't suffer from nightmares anymore. It's true I was angry at everyone involved at first, but then I started to regret killing those people- no number of deaths from my hands would bring her back. If we were to continue to carry that weight, what a world of sorrow and anger we would live in. Well, that's what I'd like to think, anyway. So, this is the item. Take this to him and tell the fella that he's welcome to visit Huigronn and we can talk about our lives. See you.

Hello. I've heard from reliable sources that you are the one who helped my sister. I hope you liked the pay... my sister is rather playful, perhaps a little too much so I hope she didn't give you a hard time. I would like to make a request of your services, would it be alright?
{c5}(With a reward, I can't see why not.){/c}
Don't worry about that. It's a common practice for my sister and I... We create outstanding items all the time. Now, my first request- I'd like you to eliminate {c1}Lipiluss Security{/c}. They are in the area to extend the power of their empire. Yet all they bring is trouble and ruin to traders and innocents in the area. I hope you take my request. When you return, I'll reward you properly. Come back soon. I have faith in your victory.

I heard many things from my sister about you but to be frank... I like the way you work. I think I should reward you with something better than what has been promised. So, do you think you'd like to do this next task?
