Ah, no. Ju-Just... No, that wouldn't work! I really liked her. When I met her back in Huigronn...  She's on my mind since then. My heart keeps pounding when I think about her, and after receiving this gift... I'm just stunned. I can't think of anything. Soldiers under my command always talk about me as being quick witted but here, what can I do? It's the first time I've felt this way. It's driving me crazy! 
