What the heart tells... hmmm, I think I get it. I'll do it that way. Why couldn't I make decisions before. I don't know what made her send me this gift. Quite a predicament, I'd say. If it's to encourage me to work hard, I'd just embarrass myself to interpret it as a token of her affection. Could you go ask her about how she feels about me? I'll be waiting... I should do this myself, but I'm in a situation.. I cannot leave here with an inspection due any day now. So, please deliver this message: "{c2}Cyrus Bearwolf{/c} really likes you so please tell me how you feel about him." Is this too forward? Anyway, tell her that and I eagerly await her reply.

