What do you want from me? Ah, you're surprised at my wings. We are different from your kind. From our records, our clan are the descendants of the high gods, Old Willow and Threemas. Though a majority of our species turned to evil, the remnants of us want peace. 
You want information on the secret of the dragon clan's power, don't you? Many explorers visit us but die because of the monsters. We want to collect their remains but it's impossible with our miniscule fighting skills.. Maybe it's possible to collect bodies if you kill the monsters first. {c5}(I'll help you guys. Could you tell me about dragon clan's power in return?){/c}
Hmmm, you got a deal! There is no reason to reject your offer since we can avoid combat all together. So. eliminate the monsters and visit us again when you're done.

Who did you say you were introduced by? Hmmm. she rarely speaks with others outside our kind. You probably have given her much assistance. Well, if you were introduced by her I know I can trust you. So, how can I help you? 
{c5}(Tell me what you know about the dragon clan's power.){/c}
Hmm... To tell you the truth, though we know more than others about this land, we don't know much about the dragons. Maybe it's because we hid from the dragons due to our appearance. I suggest you talk to our elders. I'll send a message to them. However!!! Do me a favor. I sell general goods, right? I have such a pain in my back from these spiders. Please eliminate them for my customers. I'll try to get you the information you want while you kill them. It's trade by barter... Good luck!

