Let's cut the crap. I need to make a horse saddle for the commander of the Deatheaters as soon as possible. He is going to visit soon. I have to make the best horse saddle for him before he gets here. 

It should be the best ever since he fights for us. {c2}Taceho Raksion{/c} is the best to make the horse saddle. Could you send this message to him?


{c5}Okay. I will{/c}

Hmmmm. I understand that. I could make the saddle. It's honorable. The best saddle...I need {c3}Ghostwolf's fur{/c}

{c5}What is that?{/c}

The best material for the saddle is scale of dragons, but It is even harder than winning a lottery. Anyway, the second one is {c3}Ghostwolf's fur{/c}. {c1}Ghostwolf{/c} lives in the Araky Woods. I've heard it is dreadful. I've never seen him before, but people say that his canine is almost 20 inches. 
I need {c3}Ghostwolf's fur{/c}, 50 of {c3}Amapo Spool{/c}, 30 of {c3}Poison Linz{/c}. Then I can start the work. Do you want to hunt down that creature? I guess it will be a good chance to prove how strong you are.

This is the best saddle ever! How does it look? Isn't it really cool?

{c5}It's really nice! {smile} {/c}

I'm so proud of myself. Haha. Delivery is the biggest task now. I just have one more concern.

{c5}What is that? It seems that everyhing is fine{/c}

The Goblins in Araky woods. They are ill-natured creatures. They often rob merchants of their goods and play with it. It is not possible to defeat them when so many of them attack together. That would be good for the saddle. I want you to go there and kill them all, then take this to Cfaina.
